# Falka core rules (see CLAUDE.md for full detail + code examples)

Modular-monolith: pnpm@9 + Turborepo, Node ≥20. apps/web (Next.js 15 App Router,
React 19, custom server.ts for Socket.IO), apps/worker (BullMQ), packages/* = `@falka/*`.

## TypeScript (packages/typescript-config/base.json)
strict · moduleResolution bundler · ESNext · ES2022 · isolatedModules ·
noUncheckedIndexedAccess · noImplicitOverride · verbatimModuleSyntax. Alias `@/*` → `apps/web/src/*`.
- type-only imports MUST be `import type`. Indexed access is `T | undefined` — guard it.
- DomainError subclass narrows code via `declare readonly code: XErrorCode`.

## Module boundaries (apps/web/src/modules/<feature>/)
admin · audit · auth · catalog · inventory · marketplace · notifications · orders · purchasing ·
recordings · reporting · returns · sales · scanner-pairing · storage · users.
- Cross-module talk ONLY via the other module's `services/`/`hooks/`/`validators/`/`types/`.
  Never import another module's deep internals.
- Shared logic → `@falka/*` or `apps/web/src/lib`, never duplicated per module.
- CONFLICT RULE: **preserve boundary over removing duplication** (then flag the dup).

## Folders per module
components · hooks (+`*-keys.ts`) · services (`*.service.ts`, server uses `import 'server-only'`) ·
repositories (`*.repository.ts`) · validators (Zod, +`index.ts`) · types · errors (extend
DomainError) · store (`*.store.ts`) · utils · actions · socket · config.ts. Files kebab-case.
Shared non-module: `src/lib`, `src/components`, `src/hooks`, `src/store`, `src/app/**/route.ts`.

## State
- Server state (DB/API) → **TanStack Query ONLY**; keys in `*-keys.ts`; invalidate via queryClient.
- Zustand → ONLY UI state (modal/countdown/filter/sidebar/media-stream/lifecycle).
- HARD: **no server/fetched entities in Zustand** (pairing session lives in the Query cache).

## Hard constraints — confirm BEFORE touching
Prisma schema/migrations (`packages/db/prisma/schema.prisma`) · Auth.js config
(`auth.config.ts`/`auth.ts`/`middleware.ts`) · env var names/values (`turbo.json`) ·
Socket.IO event contracts (`scanner-pairing/socket/events.ts`) · behavior of the 2 happy
flows (recording + mobile scanner).

## Quality gate — green after EVERY change
`pnpm typecheck` · `pnpm lint` (--max-warnings 0) · `pnpm build` · `pnpm test`.
No `any` · no unused · no duplication · no oversized multi-responsibility files. LF endings.

## Anti-patterns
over-engineering · server state in Zustand · business logic/Prisma in Route Handler or UI ·
cross-module deep imports · multi-responsibility files · collapsing error codes to UNKNOWN ·
console.log over logger.

## Workflow
Analyze first · incremental per-module · one logical commit per change · gates green each
commit · report bug/security/race/perf as SEPARATE suggestions · unsure → ASK (boundary > dedup).
